## ğŸ”„ 4. **Component Behavior**

| Component                               | Behavior                                             |
| --------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------- |
| `SearchBar`                             | Filters timelines by title/keywords                  |
| `CategoryFilter`, `ContradictionFilter` | Updates visible rows                                 |
| `ZoomSelector`                          | Changes timeline granularity (Year â‡„ Decade â‡„ Phase) |
| `TimelineTrack`                         | Scrollable horizontally, shows phases and events     |
| `PhaseBlock`                            | On click â†’ opens `<PhaseDetailPanel>`                |
| `EventDot`                              | On click â†’ opens `<EventDetailPanel>`                |
| `SelectedTimelineDetailsPanel`          | Opens on explicit timeline click or zoom-in          |
| `ZoomSlider`                            | Adjusts time axis scale                              |
| `TimelineScrollbar`                     | Scrolls all `<TimelineTrack>` in sync                |
| `LegendItem`                            | Static, color reference                              |

---

## ğŸ” 5. **Interaction Flows**

1. **Search / Filter / Zoom**

   * User uses top bar â†’ triggers filtering in `<TimelineCanvas>`
   * Zoom level alters phase granularity (updates `<PhaseBlock>` rendering logic)

2. **Scroll Navigation**

   * Horizontal scroll bar affects all tracks
   * Zoom slider also scales time axis across all rows

3. **Clicking PhaseBlock**

   * Loads `<PhaseDetailPanel>` with summary, events, structures, struggles

4. **Clicking EventDot**

   * Loads `<EventDetailPanel>` with full metadata, links, motion, scale, etc.

5. **Clicking Timeline Label**

   * Opens `<SelectedTimelineDetailsPanel>` for macro view

---

## ğŸ§  6. **Key UI Behavior**

| Feature             | Behavior                                          |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| Sticky Top Bar      | Top filters + zoom remain on top as user scrolls  |
| Synchronized Scroll | All timeline rows scroll together horizontally    |
| Conditional Panels  | Slide-in on trigger, stacked z-index              |
| Responsive Grid     | Rows collapse into accordion layout on mobile     |
| Tooltip on Hover    | EventDot shows headline & year                    |
| Color-coded Phases  | Indicates status: active/closed/high rupture etc. |

---

## ğŸ¨ 7. **Visual Design Guidelines**

| Design Token        | Value                                |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| Primary Font        | Inter / Roboto (Sans-serif)          |
| Timeline Row Height | 80â€“100px                             |
| EventDot Size       | 8â€“12px, circular, hover-scale: 1.25x |
| PhaseBlock Colors   | Per status (theme-light compatible)  |
| Background          | #F8F9FA (light), #212529 (dark)      |
| Panel BG            | White (light) / #1E1E1E (dark)       |
| Accent Color        | #FF6B6B (calls to action)            |
| Border Radius       | 6px (cards, buttons, panels)         |
| Padding             | 16px standard grid                   |
| Icon Set            | Tabler Icons or Bootstrap Icons      |

